<div class="doc_title">Godrej &amp; Boyce Mfg.Co.Ltd. &amp; Anr vs State Of Maharashtra &amp; Ors on 30 January, 1947</div><div class="doc_author">Author: ...….……………………..J.</div>

<div class="doc_bench">Bench: R.M. Lodha, Madan B. Lokur, Kurian Joseph</div>

<pre id="pre_1">                                                                             REPORTABLE

