           <a href="/doc/7832/" id="a_57">Acquisition Act</a>. Here also, as in the case  of  owners  of  land
           falling  under  Sub-clause  (iii)   of   <a href="/doc/998995/" id="a_58">Section   2</a>(c-i),   his
