           <a href="/doc/1792838/" id="a_59">Section 6</a> of the Acquisition Act, and this position was conceded
           by Counsel appearing for the State  of  Maharashtra.  Sub-clause
</blockquote><blockquote id="blockquote_18">           (v)  includes  within  the  definition  of  private  forest  the
